704205f-a.text: The intersection of Flatbush Avenue and Park Place at Seventh Avenue. The trolley tracks run northward on Flatbush Avenue. At the left is the Durfey house, on the corner of Seventh Avenue and Park Place; beyond it appear Nos. 8-12 Seventh Avenue and the west side of Park Place. About 1912. Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
704205f-a.folder: Flatbush Avenue & Park Place, Brooklyn, NY

704206f-a.text: 319-325 Flatbush Avenue, north side, at the intersection of Park Place and Seventh Avenue. In the foreground is a car, the Seventh Avenue Line and in the background the Flatbush Avenue Line. November, 1935. P. L. Sperr.
